== Romanian ==
=== Noun ===
'''barză'''

* [[stork]]
=== Etymology ===
Pre-Roman. Linguists such as Sorin Olteanu derive it via [[W:Dacian language|Dacian]] from [[PIE]] *bhereg-, "white". The Romanian word has a [[cognate]] in [[W:Albanian language|Albanian]], ''[[bardhë]]'', "white".

